### Presets — Deed preset management (system + family-custom)

### List all deed presets (system presets + family custom ones)
GET {{host}}/api/presets
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Create a custom deed preset — copy id from response into http-client.env.json as presetId
POST {{host}}/api/presets
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "label": "Set the table",
  "imageValue": "🍽️"
}

###

### Delete a custom deed preset (admin only; system presets are protected)
DELETE {{host}}/api/presets/{{presetId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
